{"tha-ap431:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap431:0.2":"Sakimsammajjakavagga ","tha-ap431:0.3":"9 Sovannakinkaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap431:1.1":"“Saddhaya abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap431:1.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap431:1.3":"Vakaciradharo asim, ","tha-ap431:1.4":"tapokammamapassito. ","tha-ap431:2.1":"Atthadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap431:2.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap431:2.3":"Uppajji tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap431:2.4":"tarayanto mahajanam. ","tha-ap431:3.1":"Balanca vata me khinam, ","tha-ap431:3.2":"byadhina paramena tam; ","tha-ap431:3.3":"Buddhasettham saritvana, ","tha-ap431:3.4":"puline thupamuttamam. ","tha-ap431:4.1":"Karitva hatthacittoham, ","tha-ap431:4.2":"sahatthena samokirim; ","tha-ap431:4.3":"Sonnakinkanipupphani, ","tha-ap431:4.4":"udaggamanaso aham. ","tha-ap431:5.1":"Sammukha viya sambuddham, ","tha-ap431:5.2":"thupam paricarim aham; ","tha-ap431:5.3":"Tena cetopasadena, ","tha-ap431:5.4":"atthadassissa tadino. ","tha-ap431:6.1":"Devalokam gato santo, ","tha-ap431:6.2":"labhami vipulam sukham; ","tha-ap431:6.3":"Suvannavanno tatthasim, ","tha-ap431:6.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap431:7.1":"Asitikotiyo mayham, ","tha-ap431:7.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap431:7.3":"Sada mayham upatthanti, ","tha-ap431:7.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap431:8.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap431:8.2":"bheriyo panavani ca; ","tha-ap431:8.3":"Sankha ca dindima tattha, ","tha-ap431:8.4":"vaggu vajjanti dundubhi. ","tha-ap431:9.1":"Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap431:9.2":"hatthino samalankata; ","tha-ap431:9.3":"Tidhapabhinnamatanga, ","tha-ap431:9.4":"kunjara satthihayana. ","tha-ap431:10.1":"Hemajalabhisanchanna, ","tha-ap431:10.2":"upatthanam karonti me; ","tha-ap431:10.3":"Balakaye gaje ceva, ","tha-ap431:10.4":"unata me na vijjati. ","tha-ap431:11.1":"Sonnakinkanipupphanam, ","tha-ap431:11.2":"vipakam anubhomaham; ","tha-ap431:11.3":"Atthapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap431:11.4":"devarajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap431:12.1":"Ekasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap431:12.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap431:12.3":"Pathabya rajjam ekasatam, ","tha-ap431:12.4":"mahiya karayim aham. ","tha-ap431:13.1":"So dani amatam patto, ","tha-ap431:13.2":"asankhatam sududdasam; ","tha-ap431:13.3":"Samyojanaparikkhino, ","tha-ap431:13.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap431:14.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap431:14.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap431:14.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap431:14.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap431:15.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap431:15.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap431:15.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap431:16.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap431:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap431:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap431:17.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap431:17.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap431:17.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap431:18.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sovannakinkaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap431:19.1":"Sovannakinkaniyattherassapadanam navamam. "}